description.text: Pete & Pedro Deep Cleansing Peppermint & Tea Tree Oil Shampoo Clean is our signature shampoo that contains loads of invigorating peppermint and tea tree oil to deliver big time cleanliness via a rich lather. Just a small squeeze should be more than enough to keep hair fresh, vibrant, healthy and clean like never before. We also carry Clean in travel size and XL size (saves you $7, over 10%). XL Size does not ship internationally - sorry!

The energizing peppermint scent will awaken the senses and let you know the shampoo is working hard. Tea tree oil is well-known to help remove oily build up and dead skin, and is a natural anti-fungal and antibacterial agent that works hard to rid microorganisms that thrive on the scalp and contribute to dandruff/flaking skin. Bar none the best men’s shampoo on the market. Paraben-free. Not ideal for color-treated hair.

description.text: Pete & Pedro BOLD Bourbon Shampoo is a top-shelf shampoo and one of the best men’s hair cleansers on the market. Rich and robust, the daily bourbon-scented manly but sweet shampoo is ideal for all hair types and lathers galore delivering weightless volume and strength. It smells absolutely amazing (even if you're not a whisky fan, we promise), but no gentleman, you won’t get a buzz... it doesn’t contain actual bourbon.

The shampoo is no gimmick either, it's full of incredibly healthy ingredients to keep your scalp and strands in amazing shape. Botanicals like ivy extract and panthenol condition the scalp while loads of rice protein help penetrate the hair to strengthen weak follicles. Burdock root helps make the scalp feel super-soothed and relaxed. Bar none one of the best shampoos, so try it!
